{
  "stem": "22979.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It have-- the whole city was one family, I would say, because we were living there so many, many years.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I can say that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Naturally, you know, later, everything changed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe 10-- to 20,000.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or maybe less or more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a huge cemetery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Since my mother was buried there, so, once a year, before the holidays, I went to the grave site.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a huge-- you know, with child's eyes, huge-- it's very hard to say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because later on, after the war, when I went back, it didn't seem to me so huge at all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my-- my family, grandparents, and uncles, and so were buried there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sure, it was-- I remember, my father belonged to the chevra kadisha.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- and he was a part of the community, and had some functions-- I don't know what function.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it's, you know, life in the city was nice and comfortable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's all what I can say.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my family, since they were there-- you felt-- I felt a part of this community and of this city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whenever I went on vacation visiting my family, I came back, you know, embraced everything, because it was familiar, everything.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I thought I will always live a life like we lived there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Continue in my religion-- less orthodox, because I knew for sure that my father would never allow that I will marry to another religion.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I didn't have any desire to do so even.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't envy the Christians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Although I was very curious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I know one time-- it-- I was already 13, I think so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I sneak-- because I slept many times over in my girlfriend's house, in the Christian.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
